i am experiencing very high cpu loads on the server, this was happening with 5.0.7 and i updated to 5.0.9 to see if it fixed the issue. seems to have done nothing to help.


### expected behaviour
cpu usage not 100% all the time

### actual behaviour
cpu usage is 100%

### steps to reproduce
1. start the iis server

### server configuration
operating system: windows server 2008r2

web server: iis 6.1

database: mysql

php version: 5.3.24

owncloud version: 5.0.9

### client configuration
browser: chrome

operating system: windows 7

